  "detailed_description": "<strong>Raster</strong> is a casual puzzle game about space. Here, you can use a variety of spatial abilities to traverse across diverse terrains, all in search of carrots for the bunny. For example, use the <strong>Twist</strong> ability at a high pillar that can't be crossed, and the space on both sides of the pillar will be connected! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/c330393661ecb6e1a5fccd4f8f35dacd.poster.avif?t=1762271976\" width=598 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/c330393661ecb6e1a5fccd4f8f35dacd.webm?t=1762271976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/c330393661ecb6e1a5fccd4f8f35dacd.mp4?t=1762271976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <strong><u>Features</u></strong> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🌀15+ Distinct spatial abilities </li><li>🌄15+ Scenes with different mechanics and styles </li><li>✅150+ Playable levels </li><li>🚩50+ Optional high-difficulty challenges </li><li>🏆Compete with players worldwide or friends in the leaderboard</li></ul> <strong><u>Sometimes, all it takes is simple arithmetic</u></strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/f2d485488474a47be93db54ddb133eca.poster.avif?t=1762271976\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/f2d485488474a47be93db54ddb133eca.webm?t=1762271976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/f2d485488474a47be93db54ddb133eca.mp4?t=1762271976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <strong><u>Or cutting through obstacles!</u></strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/34e650d643869594363a694f176001c5.poster.avif?t=1762271976\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/34e650d643869594363a694f176001c5.webm?t=1762271976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/34e650d643869594363a694f176001c5.mp4?t=1762271976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <strong><u>Maybe just taking photos along the way</u></strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/3270363a24307b8b6afc8381e05a1255.poster.avif?t=1762271976\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/3270363a24307b8b6afc8381e05a1255.webm?t=1762271976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586970/extras/3270363a24307b8b6afc8381e05a1255.mp4?t=1762271976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
